Feature: Search Amazon India from Google # features/amazon_search.feature:1
  As a user
  I want to search for Amazon India on Google
  So that I can validate the official Amazon homepage
  Scenario: Open the official Amazon India homepage from Google search  # features/amazon_search.feature:6
    Given the user opens Google search                                  # features/steps/amazon_search_steps.py:9
    When the user searches for "Amazon India"                           # features/steps/amazon_search_steps.py:16
    And the user clicks the official Amazon India result                # features/steps/amazon_search_steps.py:22
    Then the Amazon India homepage should load                          # features/steps/amazon_search_steps.py:28
    And the page title should contain "Amazon.in"                       # features/steps/amazon_search_steps.py:35
    And the page URL should contain "amazon.in"                         # features/steps/amazon_search_steps.py:41
    And a screenshot should be captured                                 # features/steps/amazon_search_steps.py:47

